---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { profile } from "../data/profile";
---

<BaseLayout title="About - Oscar Lares">
  <section class="section prose">
    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1 class="page-title">Data science with an engineering-first mindset.</h1>
    <p>
      I am a Data Scientist with experience across applied machine learning, analytics engineering,
      automation, and generative AI workflows. My background started in mechanical engineering, where I
      worked on mechanical design, electronics packaging, thermal analysis, and validation for aerospace
      systems.
    </p>
    <p>
      That engineering foundation now shapes how I approach data science: build practical systems, test
      assumptions, explain tradeoffs clearly, and keep the final workflow useful for the people who rely
      on it.
    </p>
    <p>
      My recent work includes automotive analytics, production ML pipelines, Snowflake/SQL data fusion,
      MLflow deployment, Dataiku workflows, and GenAI tools built with AWS Bedrock.
    </p>
    <div class="actions">
      <a class="button" href="/projects">View Projects</a>
      <a class="button secondary" href={`mailto:${profile.email}`}>Contact Me</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
